00:32:14.610 --> 00:32:16.281 align:middle line:84%
to start uplifting
again and again.

00:32:16.281 --> 00:32:18.530 align:middle line:84%
That keeps being pasted over
with these other stories.

00:32:18.530 --> 00:32:20.080 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Kind of
extraordinary, isn't it?

