mention of the Grail

00:32:29.130 --> 00:32:32.337 align:middle line:84%
appears in Sumeria,
in the song of Inanna.

00:32:32.337 --> 00:32:34.170 align:middle line:84%
And you start looking
at the priestesses who

00:32:34.170 --> 00:32:35.610 align:middle line:90%
are protecting the bloodline.

00:32:35.610 --> 00:32:38.260 align:middle line:84%
And they wore the
red robe of office.

00:32:38.260 --> 00:32:41.250 align:middle line:84%
So the priestesses had the
highest level of officialdom

00:32:41.250 --> 00:32:44.120 align:middle line:84%
in-- let's call it "religion,"
for the sake of a better word.

00:32:44.120 --> 00:32:45.786 align:middle line:84%
