"religion" because it

00:32:45.786 --> 00:32:48.350 align:middle line:84%
has all kinds of
negative connotations.

00:32:48.350 --> 00:32:50.070 align:middle line:84%
I'll say it's
spiritual religion.

00:32:50.070 --> 00:32:52.440 align:middle line:84%
And the priestesses
had the highest role

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:54.570 align:middle line:90%
in the actual temple.

00:32:54.570 --> 00:32:56.790 align:middle line:84%
Because they were in
charge of initiations

00:32:56.790 --> 00:33:00.662 align:middle line:84%
