00:33:42.900 --> 00:33:44.970 align:middle line:84%
helping the individual
find themselves,

00:33:44.970 --> 00:33:45.862 align:middle line:90%
and that connection.

00:33:45.862 --> 00:33:46.662 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Again.

