00:34:46.234 --> 00:34:47.650 align:middle line:84%
But what they were
talking about--

00:34:47.650 --> 00:34:49.670 align:middle line:84%
and they always talk in
metaphors and symbols

00:34:49.670 --> 00:34:51.540 align:middle line:84%
in these moments,
which is where we

00:34:51.540 --> 00:34:54.150 align:middle line:84%
