arguments about what's

00:34:54.150 --> 00:34:55.339 align:middle line:90%
right and wrong.

00:34:55.339 --> 00:34:57.130 align:middle line:84%
Once you start looking
at this information,

00:34:57.130 --> 00:34:59.130 align:middle line:90%
literally, you've lost the plot.

00:34:59.130 --> 00:35:01.650 align:middle line:84%
All of these people, in
order to protect themselves

00:35:01.650 --> 00:35:03.940 align:middle line:84%
and the truthfulness of what
they were trying to say,

00:35:03.940 --> 00:35:05.610 align:middle line:84%
they veiled everything
as a metaphor.

00:35:05.610 --> 00:35:07.410 align:middle line:84%
So Sion was essentially
the metaphor

00:35:07.410 --> 00:35:09.576 align:middle line:84%
for the sort of creation
of the universe.

00:35:09.576 --> 00:35:10.950 align:middle line:84%
The central point
in the universe

00:35:10.950 --> 00:35:12.510 align:middle line:90%
from where all life starts.

00:35:12.510 --> 00:35:14.310 align:middle line:84%
And from there,
once you understand

00:35:14.310 --> 00:35:17.176 align:middle line:84%
what that point does, you're
now in a very even platform.

00:35:17.176 --> 00:35:19.050 align:middle line:84%
Because if you understand
the creative points

00:35:19.050 --> 00:35:22.770 align:middle line:84%
of the sort of creation,
in all of its multiplicity,

00:35:22.770 --> 00:35:24.570 align:middle line:84%
now you can figure out
how everything else

00:35:24.570 --> 00:35:26.190 align:middle line:90%
falls into place.

00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:28.980 align:middle line:84%
If we don't understand that
you are clutching at straws.

00:35:28.980 --> 00:35:31.230 align:middle line:84%
You're getting something is
right, something is wrong.

00:35:31.230 --> 00:35:34.070 align:middle line:84%
So the points associated
with the concept of Sion

00:35:34.070 --> 00:35:37.680 align:middle line:84%
become literally the hot spots,
where this creative energy

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:39.405 align:middle line:84%
manifest on the
face of the Earth.

00:35:39.405 --> 00:35:41.280 align:middle line:84%
And this is something
that science now knows.

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:42.946 align:middle line:84%
That there are certain
spots on the face

00:35:42.946 --> 00:35:46.960 align:middle line:84%
of the Earth where energy and
gravity behaves very subtly

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:47.760 align:middle line:90%
different.

00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:48.210 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:35:48.210 --> 00:35:49.530 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: And that has
an effect on your body.

00:35:49.530 --> 00:35:50.020 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:35:50.020 --> 00:35:51.936 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: So once you
connect with that energy,

00:35:51.936 --> 00:35:54.664 align:middle line:84%
now you have become in contact
with the concept of Sion, which

00:35:54.664 --> 00:35:56.580 align:middle line:84%
