00:36:11.767 --> 00:36:13.350 align:middle line:84%
So that's what they
were tapping into.

00:36:13.350 --> 00:36:15.690 align:middle line:84%
A very old sort of
wisdom and understanding.

00:36:15.690 --> 00:36:19.560 align:middle line:84%
Of allowing you, as a physical
body, to leave that body,

00:36:19.560 --> 00:36:21.810 align:middle line:84%
